@node DESCRIPTION




  DESCRIPTION :

  It converts the "Amiga Annuaire' into text file so that Simplemail can use all E-mail directly
  (more than 600 E-mail).

@endnode

@node UTILISATION




  UTILISATION :

  Click on "SimpleMail-Converter" and give file name of "Amiga Annuaire" and destination path.
  Copy ".addressbook.xml" on SimpleMail folder.


                                  SAVE YOUR ADDRESSBOOK BEFORE !!!


  But the "Amiga annuaire" is not prepared for this. You have to modify it with Finaldata and keep only :
  Name of people and his E-mail (nothing else !)

  Example : Michel DURAND,mic.durand@free.fr (be careful to -> , )


  You must install BEFORE ! :

  - MUI (version 3.8)
  - RXMUI (version 16.6 - Freeware on http://web.tiscalinet.it/amiga/rxmui)
  - Rexxmast (in your system folder from Workbench)

@endnode

