@endnode

@node DISTRIBUTION




  DISTRIBUTION :

  FREEWARE

@endnode

@node TEST




  TEST :

  - A1260, Rom 3.0 and OS 3.0, graphic card underPicasso96, screen in 800x600 24 bits

@endnode

@node ERROR




  ERROR :

  If you have got this message : "Arithmetic conversion error"

    It means :

    - A " or ' or ) is missing in a command line
    - You have got an old RXMUI version

    An RXMUI (version 17.0) update is available at : http://web.tiscalinet.it/amiga/rxmui

@endnode
